l has been progressing speak in the field of agriculture and has added value to it. Agricultural machinery has been created in the whole world with advanced techniques and software. It is very essential for farmers and for the environment to adopt the process of digital technology for efficient and resource-friendly farming. With this technology, you can have an astonishing style of growing crops.\r\n<h3>Add value to the farming</h3>\r\nAgriculture is the complex series but it interdependent processes. Agriculture needs efficient management and organization to yield a healthy production of crops. Digital farming is the targeted management of agriculture with the use of smart electronics. Before farming of crops in digital farming, it includes electronic devices for analysis of soil degradation. This way you can check the ability of soil to grow crops. This modern technology also helps in managing spatial and temporal variability within the agricultural land.\r\n<h3>Reduce potential environment risk</h3>\r\nWhen farmers use the traditional method for farming then they use chemicals to save crops from insects. This way farmers can also improve agricultural yield and produce high-quality crops The most beneficial use of the digital farming method is to save crops from environmental risk. We all know that today due to pollution soil fertility decreases and it\'s adversely affects the growth of the crop. Besides, this advanced technology method also offers moisturizer into the soil and make a perfect balance for the optimal condition for growing plants.\r\n<h3>Offer data in real-time</h3>\r\nFarmers obtaining digital farming for producing a crop than they easily go for real-time data collection. This way they can easily analysis the report about soil fertility. The method also allows farmers to monitor the chosen parameters for ensuring accurate and update status to grow crops at the right time with the right materials. Farmers get to know about the soil condition for farming cops at the right place with full fertility.\r\n<h3>Saves time and cost</h3>\r\nWhen you opt for digital farming processes then easily save time and money. With less use of fertilizer and chemicals can easily reduce the cost of application. Even this also helps in reducing pollution through less use of chemicals and creates crops healthy and fresh. It means you do not need to waste money on purchasing chemicals and no need of paying extra time to spray chemicals. This way farmer can have a better record for sale and succession of the crop.\r\n<h3>Disadvantages of digital farming</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Digital farming refers to the regional and technology mixture farming. This needs proper information and communication technology which is not availed by all farmers. This can make digital farming risky for farmers. Without the proper knowledge, it goes for poor access and crop production.</li>\r\n 	<li>We knew that digital farming is defiance but it also brings complexity with itself. People living in rural place do not have the idea of using this strategy due to which farming system gets limited. In such an area there is a lack of electricity and also has a slow mobile connection. These are very big obstacles for rural people to cope up and opt for digital ones.</li>\r\n 	<li>Due to its highly advanced techniques and strategy, it becomes expensive for farmers. We know that digital solution is quick but to use digital technology it increases the cost of the process.</li>\r\n 	<li>It is also said that digital farming is not very suitable for small farmers as it equipped with large scale agricultural land. Farmers with large scale can easily exchange and can remain closer to the using of digital techniques.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>FAQs related to digital farming</h4>\r\n<h3>How will agriculture look in the future?</h3>\r\nWith the use of digital farming, you will get a crop production dynamic and also increases productivity. Besides, this you can also increase connectivity with digital technology.\r\n<h4>Why digital farming is important?</h4>\r\nWe all know that the environment has been changing and having pollution which damages the crop. With digital farming, you can easily produce a healthy and fresh crop.\r\n<h4>Conclusion</h4>\r\nIn sum, digital farming has been adopted by most farmers for increasing the production rate. This way you can make crops chemical-free so that you can eat fresh food. Digital farming also offers farmers to analysis their soil fertility and manages nutrition to provide it to crops. This way you can easily collect data about the whole production of the crop so that you can easily improve the quality and quantity of crop farming.','Digitalization in Farming','','publish','closed','closed','','digitalization-in-farming','','','2019-10-16 13:21:36','2019-10-16 13:21:36','',0,'https://promenadethemes.com/pt-theme-addon/?post_type=ptta-portfolio&#038;p=36',0,'ptta-portfolio','',0),(5150,1,'2017-09-15 07:21:32','2017-09-15 07:21:32','','blue-logo','','inherit','open','closed','','blue-logo','','','2017-09-15 07:21:32','2017-09-15 07:21:32','',0,'https://promenadethemes.com/demo/business-point/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/blue-logo.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(5151,1,'2017-09-19 06:55:08','2017-09-19 06:55:08','[ptta-portfolio column=\"3\"]','Our Sloutions','','publish','closed','closed','','portfolio','','','2019-10-17 09:50:41','2019-10-17 09:50:41','',0,'https://promenadethemes.com/demo/business-point/?page_id=5151',0,'page','',0),(5153,1,'2017-09-19 06:56:08','2017-09-19 06:56:08','[ptta-team image_size=\"business-point-long\" column=\"4\"]','Our Team','','publish','closed','closed','','our-team','','','2017-09-19 06:56:08','2017-09-19 06:56:08','',0,'https://promenadethemes.com/demo/business-point/?page_id=5153',0,'page','',0),(5155,1,'2017-09-19 06:56:33','2017-09-19 06:56:33','[ptta-testimonials]','Testimonials','','publish','closed','closed','','testimonials','','','2017-09-19 06:56:33','2017-0