nof interest which helps to create necessary conditions so that it could maximize\nthe production and functional food characteristics of good food. Therefore, it\nwas possible to extract the information of technology that is used by sensors\nin precision agriculture so that it may produce the low cost of food with high\ncharacteristics generated with the help of environmental care practices. The\ninformation is widely spread across the world and it is not analyzed critically\nto be complete in global vision that how the hindrance of different aspect in\nprecision agriculture</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','IY Logic','','inherit','closed','closed','','5322-revision-v1','','','2019-10-16 07:01:32','2019-10-16 07:01:32','',5322,'https://iytwist.com/2019/10/16/5322-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(5336,1,'2019-10-16 07:22:12','2019-10-16 07:22:12','','PRODUCTS','','publish','closed','closed','','products','','','2019-10-16 07:22:12','2019-10-16 07:22:12','',0,'http://iytwist.com/?page_id=5336',0,'page','',0),(5337,1,'2019-10-16 07:22:12','2019-10-16 07:22:12','','PRODUCTS','','inherit','closed','closed','','5336-revision-v1','','','2019-10-16 07:22:12','2019-10-16 07:22:12','',5336,'https://iytwist.com/2019/10/16/5336-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(5338,1,'2019-10-16 07:23:23','2019-10-16 07:23:23',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','5338','','','2019-10-23 11:57:41','2019-10-23 11:57:41','',0,'http://iytwist.com/?p=5338',3,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5339,1,'2019-10-16 07:23:23','2019-10-16 07:23:23',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','5339','','','2019-10-23 11:57:41','2019-10-23 11:57:41','',0,'http://iytwist.com/?p=5339',4,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5340,1,'2019-10-16 07:23:23','2019-10-16 07:23:23',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','5340','','','2019-10-23 11:57:41','2019-10-23 11:57:41','',0,'http://iytwist.com/?p=5340',5,'nav_menu_item','',0),(5341,1,'2019-10-16 07:35:52','2019-10-16 07:35:52','<h5><strong><i class=\"fa fa-clock-o\"></i> Business Hour