have become\nmainstreams of the adoption of other, broadband technologies and also the\nadvancement of technology .Here are some of the technologies characterizing the\nprecision agriculture trend:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>Reliable satellites for imagery and\npositioning </li><li>Low cost </li><li>Access to high internet speed </li><li>Adoption of mobile devices </li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>More than 50% farmers use the one of the precise agricultural method. </strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>What Are The Scope And Adoption Of\nPrecision Farming In India?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Adoption:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>1- Can use robots\nand small farmer machinery where the soil will not be dense and may also run on\nrenewable fuels like, compressed biogas, electricity produced on farms by\nagricultural residues and bio oil. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2- Robots are\nalready being used on small farms and it is expected that the in large scale in\nthe near future they may be deployed. Most robotic machines and drones are\nsuitable for small farms. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Precision farming in Agriculture: A game changer technology in India','','inherit','closed','closed','','5358-revision-v1','','','2019-10-16 11:35:30','2019-10-16 11:35:30','',5358,'https://iytwist.com/2019/10/16/5358-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(5361,1,'2019-10-16 11:44:07','2019-10-16 11:44:07','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Due to lots of\noptions in the market farmers face issues while selecting a farm management\nsystem. We can understand the situation so we have brought some tips to choose\nthe right one. Farming is not just an activity of growing crops. It is the\nbusiness venture and advance technology has increased its value. With farm\nmanagement system farmers can grow crops t